nd-xbox-game-pass-trial-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/starfield-no-one-pound-xbox-game-pass-trial-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/starfield-no-one-pound-xbox-game-pass-trial-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/starfield-no-one-pound-xbox-game-pass-trial-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/starfield"><em>Starfield</em></a>推出前一周，<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/microsoft">微软</a>取消了<a href="https://www.nme.com/tags/xbox-game-pass">Xbox Game Pass</a>优惠，该优惠以 1 英镑的价格向新客户介绍订阅服务。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/stalker-2-heart-of-chornobyl-preview-hands-on-3488629">《潜行者 2：切尔诺贝利之心》预览：残酷，但前景令人难以置信</a></strong></li></ul><p>据<a href="https://www.gamesradar.com/one-week-before-starfield-microsoft-quietly-kills-the-dollar1-xbox-game-pass-deal-again/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Games Radar</a>报道，玩家意识到该优惠在周末（8 月 26 日）就消失了，而且时间似乎与即将推出的<em>《Starfield》</em>有关。</p><p>最初，玩家能够以 1 英镑获得第一个月的 Xbox Game Pass，以便看到该服务的好处，例如第一天就可以玩的第一方游戏、折扣以及向后兼容<a href="https://www.nme.com/tags/xbox-360">Xbox 360</a>时代的经典游戏。</p><p>今年 3 月，Xbox 全球通讯主管卡里·佩雷斯 (Kari Perez) 表示， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/microsoft-cancels-long-running-1-game-pass-offer-3420954">该优惠已被取消</a>，因为它“[评估]未来针对新会员的不同营销促销活动”。随后，该公司推出了一个系统，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/xbox-pc-game-pass-free-trials-3438327">当前用户可以邀请五位朋友免费试用 Xbox Game Pass 两周</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3484493" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3484493" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3484493" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/starfield-preloading-starts-this-week.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/starfield-preloading-starts-this-week.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/starfield-preloading-starts-this-week-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/starfield-preloading-starts-this-week-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/starfield-preloading-starts-this-week-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/starfield-preloading-starts-this-week-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/starfield-preloading-starts-this-week-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3484493" class="wp-caption-text"> 《Starfield》来源：Xbox 游戏工作室</figcaption></figure><p>此后，该优惠在 7 月份重新启动，但一个月后，新客户的 Xbox Game Pass 有效期缩短为 14 天，价格为 1 英镑。</p><p> Xbox Game Pass 提供三个不同版本 - 主机版、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/tags/pc">PC 版</a>和旗舰版。 Ultimate 包括主机和 PC 以及 Xbox Live Gold，后者可解锁在线主机多人游戏模式以及 EA Play 中的一系列独家<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/electronic-arts">艺</a>电游戏。</p><p> As automatic monthly subscriptions, these are priced at £8.99 for console, £7.99 for PC, and £12.99 for Ultimate.</p><p> <em>Starfield</em> launches on September 6 for PC and <a href="https://www.nme.com/tags/xbox-series-xs">Xbox Series X|S</a> , yet those who have purchased the Premium or Constellation editions will be able to access the game five days earlier. </p><figure id="attachment_3249144" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3249144" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3249144" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Starfield-New-Atlantis-2000x1270-1.jpg" alt="星空。 Credit: Bethesda." width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Starfield-New-Atlantis-2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Starfield-New-Atlantis-2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Starfield-New-Atlantis-2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Starfield-New-Atlantis-2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Starfield-New-Atlantis-2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Starfield-New-Atlantis-2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3249144" class="wp-caption-text">星空。信用：贝塞斯达。</figcaption></figure><p> The sci-fi role-playing game is playable through Xbox Game Pass and if players would like to upgrade to the Premium edition for early access and bonus add-ons, like the game&#39;s first expansion, that will cost them £34.99.</p><p> In other news, <em>Starfield</em> director Todd Howard said that <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/bethesdas-todd-howard-says-talking-about-retirement-is-weird-3488033">it would be “weird” to talk about retirement</a> , but he has considered the possibility.</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/microsoft-drops-1-game-pass-deal-starfield-launch-3490207">Microsoft drops £1 Game Pass deal ahead of &#39;Starfield&#39; launch</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
